1
00:01:40,440 --> 00:01:41,240
Put me down.

2
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:46,160
The Empress is so agile.

3
00:01:47,039 --> 00:01:49,970
She truly doesn't look like someone who is pregnant.

4
00:01:50,080 --> 00:01:50,880
You found out.

5
00:01:52,520 --> 00:01:54,200
I've been thinking about it all the way here,

6
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:56,400
but I can't figure out who the father is.

7
00:01:57,360 --> 00:02:00,280
I'm glad you didn't misunderstand my relationship with Prince Qi.

8
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:01,520
Except for Li Yunmo.

9
00:02:05,840 --> 00:02:07,240
He is like a brother to me.

10
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:08,139
A close friend.

11
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:10,860
Let's not talk about this.

12
00:02:11,160 --> 00:02:12,600
Don't blame the Imperial Physician.

13
00:02:12,600 --> 00:02:13,660
I made him say that.

14
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:14,880
I know.

15
00:02:15,320 --> 00:02:15,960
You know?

16
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:19,760
Your Majesty.

17
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:22,320
Her Majesty's pulse is stable,

18
00:02:22,600 --> 00:02:25,200
but she asked me to lie for her.

19
00:02:25,480 --> 00:02:28,600
I am of humble status and could not refuse.

20
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:32,360
This Wang Zhen...

21
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:34,440
is really a shrewd one.

22
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:35,600
But,

23
00:02:36,040 --> 00:02:37,680
why did you fake it?

24
00:02:38,320 --> 00:02:38,920
[Confess]

25
00:03:18,920 --> 00:03:19,720
So,

26
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:23,130
who on earth are you guarding against?

27
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:24,160
No one.

28
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:26,970
You know I'm faking pregnancy.

29
00:03:27,079 --> 00:03:28,079
Aren't you angry?

30
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:29,360
Angry?

31
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:32,410
A husband follows his wife.

32
00:03:32,880 --> 00:03:34,079
No matter what you do,

33
00:03:34,320 --> 00:03:35,380
I will support you.

34
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:36,360
Since you want to put on an act,

35
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,680
I'll play along with you.

36
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:39,160
So what happened exactly?

37
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:41,920
If I tell Li Yunxi,

38
00:03:42,160 --> 00:03:43,240
Hanxing might die.

39
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:46,600
I should ask Father about the Ghost Face first.

40
00:03:48,920 --> 00:03:50,650
I'm suffocating in the palace.

41
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:53,120
I want to visit the military camp tomorrow.

42
00:03:53,320 --> 00:03:54,380
The military camp?

43
00:04:02,600 --> 00:04:03,530
Why are you here?

44
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:05,200
I'm going with you.

45
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:07,200
Su Kuang.

46
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:08,520
My Lady.

47
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:16,250
Who will handle your official duties?

48
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:19,640
All the court officials have holidays.

49
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:20,480
Why don't I?

50
00:04:21,320 --> 00:04:22,480
I am human too.

51
00:04:23,080 --> 00:04:24,160
I get tired too.

52
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:27,720
The false Xuanniao faction is still at large.

53
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:29,400
Assassins are everywhere outside.

54
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:32,060
It's dangerous for Li Yunxi to leave the palace.

55
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:33,159
No.

56
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:35,380
You must return to the palace.

57
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:36,120
Go.

58
00:04:36,760 --> 00:04:38,520
The army is full of your old troops. It's safe.

59
00:04:38,520 --> 00:04:39,400
Still no.

60
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:39,920
Go.

61
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:41,320
I'm going.

62
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:42,120
Go.

63
00:04:42,400 --> 00:04:42,920
I'm going.

64
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:43,400
Let's go.

65
00:04:43,400 --> 00:04:43,800
I'm going.

66
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:44,040
Go.

67
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:44,840
Your Majesty.

68
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:50,480
Why are you here?

69
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:53,010
Since Your Majesty and the Empress are going,

70
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:54,300
I want to go as well.

71
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:04,400
Su Kuang, let's go.

72
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,420
Yes, Your Majesty.

73
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:20,840
Stop pushing me.

74
00:05:20,840 --> 00:05:22,240
Can't you move over a bit?

75
00:05:22,440 --> 00:05:23,280
It's such a small space.

76
00:05:23,280 --> 00:05:24,680
Where am I supposed to go?

77
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:26,040
Your Majesty, come over here.

78
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:27,440
I don't mind the squeeze.

79
00:05:30,080 --> 00:05:31,840
I didn't expect Father to be busy with military duties

80
00:05:31,840 --> 00:05:33,480
and unable to return to the camp until tomorrow.

81
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:35,010
Let's wait until tomorrow.

82
00:05:37,280 --> 00:05:38,210
Why are you here?

83
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:42,120
Didn't you ask me to come?

84
00:05:43,200 --> 00:05:44,280
I invited you.

85
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:47,600
Cousin, we haven't seen each other for a long time.

86
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:48,680
I rarely get out of the Palace,

87
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:50,680
so I sent someone to invite you over.

88
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:56,720
Why didn't you tell me you were leaving the Palace?

89
00:05:58,840 --> 00:06:00,280
I am only considerate

90
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:01,930
and patient with you

91
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:03,800
because you are the one I love.

92
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:06,160
Prince Qi.

93
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:08,940
I just came out of the Palace for a stroll.

94
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:10,960
I didn't want to disturb anyone.

95
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:11,960
Prince Qi.

96
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:14,050
Why do these words sound

97
00:06:14,760 --> 00:06:16,040
so distant?

98
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:22,850
Not distant.

99
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:28,480
Perhaps,

100
00:06:30,400 --> 00:06:32,330
I should call him Brother-in-law.

101
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:45,520
Your Majesty.

102
00:06:46,200 --> 00:06:47,460
It's too cold tonight.

103
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:49,200
Let's go back to our room.

104
00:06:51,080 --> 00:06:52,640
Who told you to wear so little?

105
00:06:52,640 --> 00:06:53,720
If you're cold, go back yourself.

106
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:55,650
If I'd known the camp was this cold,

107
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:57,200
I would have worn a cloak.

108
00:06:57,760 --> 00:06:59,200
Ling, are you cold?

109
00:06:59,760 --> 00:07:00,420
No, I'm not.

110
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:04,480
Of course you're not cold, wearing so much.

111
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:04,920
Here.

112
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:07,820
Drink some wine to warm up.

113
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:08,520
Thank you.

114
00:07:26,280 --> 00:07:27,040
Cousin.

115
00:07:27,760 --> 00:07:29,760
Now that Her Majesty is pregnant,

116
00:07:30,440 --> 00:07:31,640
she shouldn't drink.

117
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:37,200
Pregnant?

118
00:07:51,520 --> 00:07:52,080
Li Yunxi,

119
00:07:52,880 --> 00:07:53,810
go back to sleep.

120
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:12,760
Ling, why are you sleeping with me tonight?

121
00:08:12,760 --> 00:08:13,600
Get away.

122
00:08:28,400 --> 00:08:31,260
I asked them to prepare the best bedding in the army,

123
00:08:32,159 --> 00:08:33,559
not the reddest.

124
00:08:36,919 --> 00:08:38,000
It's good.

125
00:08:49,160 --> 00:08:50,720
Are you not angry anymore?

126
00:08:53,520 --> 00:08:54,360
I'm not angry.

127
00:08:57,280 --> 00:08:59,880
Ever since I took Liu Mianmian as my concubine,

128
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:02,360
we have grown apart.

129
00:09:03,640 --> 00:09:04,760
Li Yunxi's memory

130
00:09:05,160 --> 00:09:07,160
is still stuck in the time after our wedding,

131
00:09:07,160 --> 00:09:09,290
when we were at odds over Liu Mianmian.

132
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:11,800
I'm sorry.

133
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:15,040
I knew you weren't the type

134
00:09:16,280 --> 00:09:18,480
to be willing to share.

135
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:24,020
I'll sleep on the small couch.

136
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:30,200
Yunxi.

137
00:09:30,680 --> 00:09:32,010
No matter what happens,

138
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:33,680
I love you.

139
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:36,020
Even if we torture each other,

140
00:09:36,640 --> 00:09:38,360
we'll be together forever.

141
00:09:39,520 --> 00:09:40,600
No one escapes.

142
00:09:41,560 --> 00:09:43,560
We'll be together even in death.

143
00:09:48,280 --> 00:09:48,800
Ling,

144
00:09:49,880 --> 00:09:51,360
if you knew the truth,

145
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:53,800
would you still say that?

146
00:10:14,920 --> 00:10:15,400
Master.

147
00:10:17,520 --> 00:10:18,280
You want to intensify

148
00:10:18,280 --> 00:10:20,480
the conflict between the Xiao Army and the Emperor

149
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:22,280
and make them turn on each other.

150
00:10:22,640 --> 00:10:24,480
There's no need to harm Her Ladyship.

151
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:26,280
You've gone soft on Xiao Ling.

152
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:29,100
The child is innocent.

153
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:35,180
It is not your place to comment on my affairs.

154
00:10:35,400 --> 00:10:35,880
Leave.

155
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:50,450
Who exactly are you?

156
00:11:23,400 --> 00:11:24,530
You didn't pass out.

157
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:26,040
Of course.

158
00:11:26,920 --> 00:11:27,560
I didn't.

159
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:46,970
What is this?

160
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:54,000
I wanted to personally make an undergarment

161
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:55,530
for Your Highness's child.

162
00:11:59,640 --> 00:12:00,240
Hanxing.

163
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:03,330
Your feelings for me

164
00:12:04,480 --> 00:12:06,080
weren't all fake, were they?

165
00:12:11,680 --> 00:12:12,480
Who is he?

166
00:12:15,880 --> 00:12:18,140
So Your Highness suspected me all along.

167
00:12:18,400 --> 00:12:19,260
You did all this

168
00:12:19,760 --> 00:12:21,240
just to lure out my master.

169
00:12:22,160 --> 00:12:23,360
I won't say anything.

170
00:12:34,920 --> 00:12:36,080
From today on,

171
00:12:37,840 --> 00:12:39,900
we have nothing to do with each other.

172
00:12:40,240 --> 00:12:42,100
You need not return to the palace.

173
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:44,520
Go serve your master.

174
00:12:49,560 --> 00:12:50,420
Your Highness.

175
00:12:53,600 --> 00:12:54,280
Hanxing.

176
00:12:55,120 --> 00:12:57,080
You are the only family I have left.

177
00:12:57,640 --> 00:12:59,280
I will protect you.

178
00:12:59,760 --> 00:13:01,690
I can't let anything happen to you.

179
00:13:01,880 --> 00:13:03,280
There is no need to hurt Her Highness.

180
00:13:03,280 --> 00:13:04,280
The child is innocent.
